nt=wp2fa\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Official Melapress website<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3>Installing WP 2FA<\/h3>\n<h3>From within WordPress<\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Navigate to \u2018Plugins &gt; Add New\u2019<\/li>\n<li>Search for \u2018WP 2FA\u2019<\/li>\n<li>Install &amp; activate WP 2FA from your Plugins page<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<h3>Manually<\/h3>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin from the WordPress plugins repository<\/li>\n<li>Unzip the zip file and upload the folder to the \/wp-content\/plugins\/ directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the WP 2FA plugin through the \u2018Plugins\u2019 menu in WordPress<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
